cause: Faulty cable (+TOW-W10) from CB):X5 to CTO:X5
actions: Check resistance between wires X5:1,2,3 and cable insulation of +TOW-W10 wire no. 1,2,3 in the bottom cabinet.
questions: Is any of the following circuit breaker tripped?
questionAnswers: 230V AC pitch supply breaker (-2F3) tripped in top cabinet (CTO).
3 x 230V AC pitch supply breaker (-10F1) tripped in bottom cabinet (CBO).
3 x 400V AC pitch supply breaker (-33F1) tripped in bottom cabinet (CBO).

All three digital inputs 88, 89 and 90 DIi_Pit1_EmergencyRun recorded true at the same time.
